(7, 'EdTech', '<p>Educational software development involves building LMS, <a href=\"https://radixweb.com/case-studies/online-training-portal\">eLearning portals</a>, course management systems, and mLearning solutions for academic institutions, enterprises, and edtech companies. Our professionals offer advanced expertise and know-how to build scalable architectures for edtech using modern technologies in web, mobile, databases, and cloud. Leverage 25+ market tested EdTech solutions with end-to-end assistance from ‘The Experts’ of Inbox Infotech.</p>', '<p>Experience ‘Innovation’ and ‘Excellence’ for your custom eLearning development project with guidance from Radixweb’s dependable and disruption-ready team of education software developers. Our domain experts demonstrate profound know-how of modern technologies and market-tested practices for developing captivating and immersive eLearning experiences.</p><p>We are an educational software development company with relentless pursuit towards crafting innovative EdTech solutions that brings tangible benefits. 93% tech leaders consistently entrusted our <a href=\"https://radixweb.com/services/custom-software-development\">custom software development</a> expertise across industries for 2x returns on investment. In fact, we have 30 steady businesses with 5+ years of engagement ratio. These strong relationships are nurtured through open conversations, radical transparency, and solution-focused approach.</p><p>Confidently scale the peaks of $198.2 billion eLearning industry with tech innovations that perennially transforms boring classrooms and traditional textbook education.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1745495649.png', NULL, NULL, 'EdTech', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'aadil', 'aadil', '1', NULL, '2025-04-23 10:53:15', '2025-04-24 11:54:09'),
(8, 'InsurTech', '<p>Amplify your insurance service offerings with diverse insurance software development services. Make claims simplified, streamline policy management, encrypt secure transactions, and customize user experiences with exceptional customer support.</p>', '<h2><strong>Navigate the Complexities of Insurtech with Digitally Advanced Solutions</strong></h2><p>Speed, accuracy, optimum productivity, and responsiveness are crucial to the insurance industry. With our two decades of experience in developing bespoke solutions, we harp at reshaping the operational efficiencies of firms like yours as you progress towards meeting the demands of the rapidly evolving market.</p><p>We thoroughly understand the complexities of the insurance industry, our tailored approach towards addressing insurance industry needs have optimized operations and reshaped client experiences for numerous firms. We use new-age technologies like ML, AI, and data analytics to build software that doesn’t just address immediate needs but places insurance firms ahead of complexities that might develop in the future.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1745495786.png', NULL, NULL, 'InsurTech', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'aadil', 'aadil', '1', NULL, '2025-04-23 10:56:15', '2025-04-24 11:56:26'),
(9, 'CleanTech', '<p>Build innovative, scalable and custom solutions across renewable energy, climate tech, circular economy, e-mobility. Empower a sustainable tech future with sustainability roadmaps to meet regulatory compliances.</p>', '<p>We make technology an enabler in sustainable resource usage. Our engineers have deep expertise in industrial design and data engineering. Paired with our intelligence in power management, process monitoring and heating control - we help you <a href=\"https://radixweb.com/services/cloud-application-development\">develop cloud-led apps</a> that aren’t just sustainable but functional as well.</p><p>Leveraging software modernization with cleantech, we help you eliminate integration challenges across cleantech ecosystems. We also implement Big data and Gen AI automation to improve energy efficiency for your enterprise.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1745405884.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'CleanTech', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'aadil', 'aadil', '1', NULL, '2025-04-23 10:58:04', '2025-04-24 04:34:59');
