(2, 'Mobile Applications', '<p>Take your <a href=\"https://inboxtechs.com/services/Mobile-Applications-Development\">mobile application</a> to the next level by exploring our customized mobile app solutions. With Inbox Infotech, experience the power of working with an extremely proficient and knowledgeable team of application developers. Offering integrated <a href=\"https://inboxtechs.com/services/Mobile-Applications-Development\">app development</a> solutions for both Android and iOS platforms, we are where your dream meets reality.</p>', '<h3><strong>What do We offer?</strong></h3><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Whether it\'s design, integration, delivery to maintenance; we ensure that a high-quality and fully secure mobile app is delivered to you well within the decided timeline. From business consulting, mobile app design, and custom app development, to marketing and promotion—we got you covered.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>Why Choose This Service?</strong></h4><p><br><strong>Increase wide-scale accessibility | Transform the usability experience | Improved connection with customers | Strengthen brand image | Offer improvised value to the customers | Nurture customer loyalty</strong></p><p><br><strong>What is the usual process of mobile app development?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The usual process of a <a href=\"https://inboxtechs.com/services/Web-Development\">web development company</a> is fairly a standardized one and includes mobile app designing, development, and deployment along with a few processes involved post its launch.</p><p><br><strong>On what platforms can you avail mobile application development from Inbox Infotech?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Inbox Infotech offers mobile application development on Android and iOS platforms.</p><p><br><strong>How many days does it take to design and develop a mobile app?</strong></p><p><br>It takes a period of 14-20 days to design and develop a mobile app. However, the tenure deems to vary according to the complexity of the app.