(3, 'AI/ML', '<p>Enhance creativity and unlock new possibilities with the artificial intelligence services of Inbox Infotech solutions. Our AI capabilities are embedded in the software to offer you automated and intelligent solutions. Our AI technologies support a diverse environment including machine learning, computer vision, forecasting and optimization, and natural language processing. Value our technologies are true to meet the changing business needs.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://inboxtechs.com/services/Machine-Learning\">Machine learning</a> programs can perform tasks without being explicitly programmed to do so. It involves computers learning from data provided so that they carry out certain tasks. For simple tasks assigned to computers, it is possible to program algorithms telling the machine how to execute all steps required to solve the problem at hand; on the computer\'s part, no learning is needed. For more advanced tasks, it can be challenging for a human to manually create the needed algorithms. In practice, it can turn out to be more effective to help the machine develop its own algorithm, rather than having human programmers specify every needed step.</p>', '<h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><p><br>For the first time, we have a technology that is pervasive in nature. This can be infused into and transform your business model, the processes that define it, the applications that deliver it, and the infrastructure that supports it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>Why Choose This Service</strong></h4><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Advanced AI algorithms | Data and data management | Digital Assistance | Computational systems | Reduce human error | 24/7 Support</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>What are the common examples of AI technologies?</strong></h4><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Common examples of AI technologies are speech recognition, national language understanding, and dialogue management/conversational AI.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>What are AI services?</strong></h4><p><br>Artificial intelligence refers to basically a third party that offers artificial intelligence outsourcing. There are multiple <a href=\"https://inboxtechs.com/services/Cloud-Services\">Cloud AI service providers</a> that offer specialized hardware as needed for AI tasks including GPU-based processing facilitating intensive workloads.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>What are the popular 3 kinds of AI?</strong><br>The popular kinds of AI are artificial narrow intelligence, artificial general intelligence, and artificial super intelligence.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1745408699.png', 'artificial-intelligence', NULL, 'fab fa-500px', 'Amplify your business with Inbox Infotech by using AI in every aspect of your business, democratizing AI responsibly', 'Artificial-Intelligence-services', NULL, NULL, 'shyam', 'aadil', '1', NULL, '2022-10-10 01:41:08', '2025-04-23 11:44:59'),
(4, 'Recruitment & Staffing', '<p>Inbox Infotech provides end-to-end recruitment and staffing solutions, helping businesses find the right talent quickly and efficiently. Our services include permanent hiring, contract staffing, and workforce management tailored to diverse industry needs.</p>', '<h3><strong>What do We offer?</strong></h3><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Transform business processes into intelligent autonomous ones with the help of the machine learning services of Inbox Infotech. Offering both supervised, semi-supervised and unsupervised machine learning on structured and unstructured data, the services are aims at building, training, validating, the optimize, deploying, and testing machine learning models with the help of tools and technologies.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>Why Choose This Service?</strong></h4><p><br><strong>Simplify product marketing | Facilitate easier detection of spam | Accurate sales forecasts | Simplify data entry documentation | Customer segmentation | Upgrade precision pertaining to financial rules</strong></p><p><br><strong>How is machine learning different from deep learning?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Deep learning refers to a subfield of representation learning which a subfield of machine learning is. Deep learning, distinct from that machine learning extracts features automatically from the raw data and becomes efficient.</p><p><br><strong>What is machine learning?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Machine learning is the system’s ability to comprehend a task without explicitly being programmed from a given data.</p><p><br><strong>What are the four kinds of machine learning algorithms?</strong></p><p><br>The four distinct kinds of machine learning algorithms are supervised algorithms, non-supervised algorithms, semi-supervised algorithms, and reinforcement learning algorithms</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1745408803.png', 'Machine Learning', NULL, 'fas fa-diagnoses', 'Machine learning is a field of inquiry devoted to understanding and building methods that \'learn\', that is, methods that leverage data to improve performance on some set of tasks. It is seen as a part of artificial intelligence.', 'recruitment staffing', NULL, NULL, 'shyam', 'aadil', '1', NULL, '2022-10-10 02:49:24', '2025-04-23 12:53:46'),
(5, 'Infrastructure Management', '<p>Inbox Infotech helps enterprises accelerate their digital transformation with our comprehensive suite of offerings that covers the entire IT infrastructure stack. With our platform-enabled solutions powered by AI and Automation, we help enterprises accelerate their journey to a digital future. Our focus is on helping organizations develop a future-ready infrastructure aligned with their core business needs.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', '<h4>What We Offer</h4><p>With Inbox Infotech, the digital age can be easily conquered. Inbox InfoTech’s infrastructure management solutions offer a consolidated end-to-end view of the applications and infrastructure. Offering an integrated dashboard, we enable our clients to monitor the network infrastructure, applications, servers along with other components to optimize IT performance. The proven automation tools essentially standardize operations and eliminate all manual processes while improving accuracy and precision.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>Why Choose This Service</strong></h4><p><br>Inbox Infotech’s Infrastructure &amp; Cloud Services cover the entire Infrastructure stack and support new-age technologies that can help enterprises embrace a truly digital transformation:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Boost productivity | Using the best of technology | Improved centralized management | Low capital outlay | Reduced downtime | Expert analysis of Infrastructure</strong></p><p><br><strong>What are the primary components of an IT infrastructure?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The primary components of an IT infrastructure are storage, network, and computing.</p><p><br><strong>Why is infrastructure management important?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Infrastructure management essentially plays a major role in shaping the future and offers improved processes and policies which need to be adhered to.</p><p><br><strong>What are the crucial domains of a typical IT infrastructure?</strong></p><p><br>The crucial domains of an IT infrastructure are the user domain, a LAN domain, a WAN domain, a remote access domain, Lan to a WAN domain, an application domain, and many others.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1745409424.jpg', 'Infrastructure Management', NULL, 'far fa-window-restore', 'Inbox Infotech’s Infrastructure Service covers the entire Infrastructure stack and supports new age technologies.', 'Infrastructure-Management', NULL, NULL, 'shyam', 'aadil', '1', NULL, '2022-10-10 03:41:26', '2025-04-23 11:57:04'),
(6, 'Cloud Services', '<p>Let a single provider seamlessly and securely connect to diverse cloud solutions. Our industry-leading partnerships let you grow your business, its efficiency, and productivity. The services are catered to helping build an agile IT ecosystem using hybrid multi-cloud environments, networks, and security that is required globally. The world-class solutions enable to expand across the globe and improve efficiency and productivity while delivering seamless customer experience.</p>', '<h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Inbox Infotech’s Infrastructure &amp; Cloud Services cover the entire Infrastructure stack and support new-age technologies that can help enterprises embrace a truly digital transformation.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>Why Choose This Service</strong></h4><p><br><strong>Improved data security | Higher scalability | Disaster recovery management | Greater mobility | Improved control over data | Cost reduction</strong></p><p><br><strong>What are the common kinds of cloud services?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The usage of cloud services is associated with common cloud offerings that include software as a service, and infrastructure as a service.</p><p><br><strong>Is the cloud safe to be used?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Yes, the cloud is extremely safe to be used as the data stays extremely safe inside the cloud. It is a lot safer as compared to a hard drive.</p><p><br><strong>Can my cloud data be seen by anybody?</strong></p><p><br>The data is visible to only people with whom you have shared access to view it. Thus, access needs to be given only to those who can be trusted.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1745409095.png', 'Cloud Service', NULL, 'fab fa-cloudsmith', 'By combining a comprehensive suite of cloud offerings across the Cloud lifecycle, we provide our clients a unique transformation roadmap aligned to their business goals.', 'Cloud-Services', NULL, NULL, 'shyam', 'aadil', '1', NULL, '2022-10-10 01:5