r business', 'UX-and-UI-Design', NULL, NULL, 'shyam', 'Human Resource', '0', NULL, '2022-10-10 03:47:31', '2023-12-28 04:06:40'),
(17, 'E-Commerce', '<p>Offering easy navigation and an engaging interface, Inbox Infotech offers e-commerce business solutions that facilitate an administrator with easy management facilities at Inbox Infotech. We are a certified <a href=\"https://inboxtechs.com/products/E-Commerce\">eCommerce website development company</a> that aims to take care of all criteria for the development services of the online store. Offering eCommerce hosting solutions, we develop a customized and secured online eCommerce store. Entrust our services for an agile-driven eCommerce website solution.</p>', '<h3><strong>What do We offer?</strong></h3><p>&nbsp;</p><p>With an experienced team of web developers, engineers, UI/UX designers, and content strategists; we’ll choose the perfect platform, give your products an extra edge and create an e-commerce website with a quick and responsive design that is both web and mobile friendly.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>Why Choose This Service?</strong></h3><p><br><strong>Streamline production and service delivery | Simplify sales and marketing | Save time and costs | Pleasant customer experience | Stay competitive | Lowered costs</strong></p><p><br><strong>What kind of customer service is offered?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The eCommerce consultants answer all queries related to your eCommerce website.</p><p><br><strong>Can the e-Commerce website be used with my own domain name?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The e-Commerce website can be used with your own domain name and you can simply point the domain directly to the new Network Solutions Ecommerce. There is no need to use a subdomain or any temporary one.</p><p><br><strong>How will shoppers be able to find my eCommerce store?</strong></p><p><br>With the help of SEO experts and strategies, potential shoppers are able to find your store.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1672718819.webp', 'E-Commerce', NULL, 'fas fa-shopping-cart', 'Our wide-ranging solutions address all customer needs. Inbox Infotech is amongst Ecom\'s top Global Strategic Service Partners.', 'E-Commerce', NULL, NULL, 'shyam', 'Human Resource', '0', NULL, '2022-10-10 03:52:50', '2023-12-28 04:06:57'),
